  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Venlafaxine Extended Release in Elderly Depressed Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Vandral Retard (Venlafaxine Extended Release) in Depressive Syndrome With Anxiety and Painful Symptoms in Elderly Patients. Observational Study in Primary Care</official_title>
  <sponsors>
