  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In this study we will assess as a primary objective the effect of venlafaxine retard
      treatment on primary care attended elderly patients with depressive syndrome. We will also
      study secondarily its effects on anxiety, somatic and painful symptoms of depression.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
